src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門只係強國一條村ja<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇嚟你閱讀能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定你想偷換概念，我唔知啦<br />\n<br />\n我指利用澳門係「利用澳門發生今次嘅事件」，唔係利用澳門人或者澳門啲乜嘢組織<br />\n政治就係利用，指嘅係我要宣傳依賴支那電力幾差嘅，我可以利用澳門今次斷電嘅事嚟宣傳，依個已經係一個例子<br />\n好簡單，一百個人對事件有一百個理解，講一句嘢點描述已經係政治宣傳，特別係網絡平台"},{"pid":"1ac8d7067b53e13e6c1f6eb5384c74c706774bc5","tid":374988,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d 野香港政黨玩到爛晒<br />\n澳門西出事就想痴埋來呃香港人幫你製造輿論壓力<br />\n過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政治係互相利用<br />\n有用就用，冇用就唔用<br />\n澳門事件對反中係有利嘅事<br />\n唔發生都發生咗<br />\n分別係在於點利用嚟政治宣傳</blockquote><br />\n互相利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政治冇永遠嘅朋友"},{"pid":"56a060681d4e9b3af67fd4e7e5bb7fcd6bedef97","tid":374988,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69ed43c6e716aff9c6e52e998b3cb866c924fab","tid":374988,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3533a60eeb33eaf03618eb8af7cd483043a20258","tid":374988,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f82d458e24dad6d0aaa6f54971dfdef96932518","tid":374988,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}